Dvds were sent just as described, promptly and in good condition. Was a gift and has been enjoyed very much.

When the metal box containing the disc arrived I noted the disc said Time-Life on the label.  It turns out that the Garth Brooks DVDs had been replaced by country western CDs.  The seller automatically credited my account and told me to keep the CDs.  How nice to deal with folks that make an unintentional error "right" without a hassle.
Garth Brooks - The EntertainerBoxed DVD set shipped extremely fast and in great condition!
This was the best deal we ever got on Amazon and we really enjoyed it.
I normally do not care for country music but, this album set blew my socks off!!!  I'm a convert.

I really don't think Garth needs a review from someone like him...  He is the ultimate entertainer!  I only wish to see him in concert at least once before he retires again.  Till then, this will have to suffice!

just got the set....only listened to 10 minutes of the dvd I bought the set for, the central park concert, am very disappointed so far, the concert is missing 20+ mins of what they showed on HBO live, the dvd is heavily edited lots of the in-between songs stuff is missing, plus the audio is horrible, I have a vhs copy of the samething from when it was showed live and the sound is 10x better, and that's saying something cause its a VHS tape, I hope the rest of the discs are not the same poor quality, if this set was for walmart only that would explain the bad quality because that's ALL you get from walmart....its certainly not worth 99 bucks Amazon wants retail for it, heck its not worth what I paid for it let alone full retail
This DVD set is fantastic!  I highly encourage Garth Brooks' fans to order this product!!
